2. Hypothesis: PRODUCT ANALYTICS HYPOTHESIS FRAMEWORK: EMOTIONAL TRIGGERS & CHURN
=============================================================================

1. Identify the Emotional Triggers
   - Frustration: The game demands more skill than the player has. They feel 
     cheated, overwhelmed, or stuck.
   - Boredom: The player has more skill than the game demands. There is no 
